headline: GoDaddy Agency: A New Way to Help Digital Consultants Grow
summary: GoDaddy (NYSE: GDDY) today announced the launch of GoDaddy Agency, a new partner program connecting digital agencies with small and mid-sized business leads and access to comprehensive tools, services and support to grow their client offerings.
